<p class="c6" id="h.3o7alnk"><span class="c11 c22">We respect the choice of the opportunity owner to add or remove members from its team. In case of any dispute between the opportunity owner and one or more team members, this would be addressed off-line by the Team member themselves. Connecting Talents is not accountable for any dispute or litigation between members that must be solved off-line. For statistical reason, we would like to be informed via our contact channels so that we might have the chance to support you on voluntary basis and fine-tune our matching algorithms.</span>
